section.p:
All variants of this base image, for different text directions, sizes, and states, are available from this icon bundle. An AWT or Swing component may be passed to the icon bundle to provide hints as to e.g. selection colors for the image.
JComponent label = new JLabel();
Image rtlNormal48x48 = iconBundle.getImage(label, IconTextDirection.RIGHT_TO_LEFT, IconState.NORMAL, IconSize.DEFAULT_48X48);
Image ltrSelected32x32 = iconBundle.getImage(label, IconTextDirection.LEFT_TO_RIGHT, IconState.SELECTED, IconSize.DEFAULT_32X32);
Image ltrMouseover16x16 = iconBundle.getImage(label, IconTextDirection.LEFT_TO_RIGHT, IconState.SELECTED, IconSize.DEFAULT_16X16);
